en - Typologie, Chronologie, Inszenierung und Komposition - im internationalen Rahmen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAusstellung. 4aGeschichte. 4aGestaltung. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aKunst. 4aMuseumspädagogik. 4aMuseumswissenschaft. 7aART / Museum Studies.2bisacsh  aArts.  aCultural Studies.  aMuseology.  aMuseum Education.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Kunst Arch. 2000-2009z9783110463378oZDB-23-TKA0 cprintz978389942192740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839401927?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839401927423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839401927/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TKAc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009